{"tid":411234,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple 為 App Store 新界西推出四個廣告","createTime":"2017-09-23T15:51:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T09:44:01.000Z","uid":40198,"like":4,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a7c0f3e453ee2af68a8c1684f115f8e88642b2f","tid":411234,"uid":40198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T15:51:43.000Z","msg":"iOS 11 更新後多了不同特別功能，這些不同功能相信大家都經已使用過。但你可能最缺少認識的就是 iOS 11 中的 App Store 了，不難發現 App Store 的改變跟過去相比的改變更為大，甚至 Apple 這次就單單為了 App Store 重點推出了四個不同廣告，以簡單介紹一下 App Store 的改變跟過往的不同。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於這次 App Store 的更新中，由介面主題到內容顯示方式，都較過往的不同。特別在於主要劃分為 Today、遊戲、應用程式的選項，告別了過往的精選項目、類別及排行榜。這次四條廣告擁有分別有 1 段長 38 秒，3 段長 15 秒，全都是在介紹新 App Store 的介面，及 App Store 當中的精彩內容，主要圍繞著尋找藝術文化 App、購物 App、遊戲 App，多項不同應用程式。相信這次新的 App Store 界面到來，一眾用家亦要重新適應了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/09/22/apple-10/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F09%2F22%2Fapple-10%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=wEpdz9VwhN%2Bl139cOmf2NtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=a5180a71\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/09/22/apple-10/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"1baeb56675d3742f9726ff2cf908fc612fb457a0","tid":411234,"uid":16880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"新界西"},{"pid":"815bccae68cc2319d4af64f5e974c5d2fab031ce","tid":411234,"uid":132825,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T15:56:27.000Z","msg":"卑個新界西呃左入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc6476c2717d4d5cc6af922670d0ed117e5a41b","tid":411234,"uid":2059,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T15:57:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>卑個新界西呃左入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲諗緊關新界西咩事...."},{"pid":"d467ce6f1fd3dd0f1289fd4c79cc8f5d437dcd6b","tid":411234,"uid":41472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T15:58:39.000Z","msg":"新乜嘢界西